inputFiles.beam.dat:
RNDSEED      	89736501     ! Random seed
JPART0       	2            ! Incident particle type
TMAX0      	200.0  1.5       ! Incident energy; (MeV/nucl)
NSTAT       10000    0       ! NSTAT, Step of saving
STRAGG          2            ! Straggling: 0-Off 1-Gauss, 2-Vavilov
MSCAT           2            ! Mult. scatt 0-Off 1-Gauss, 2-Moliere
NUCRE           1            ! Nucl.Reac. switcher: 1-ON, 0-OFF
BEAMPOS 0 18 0 ! Position of the beam
BEAMDIR 90.0 270.0 ! Direction of the beam
inputFiles.detect.dat:
Geometry Mesh
    Name Detect
    X -0.5 0.5 1
    Y -20 20 400
    Z -10 10 200

Filter
    Name protons
    A == 1
    Z == 1
Filter
    Name primary
    Z == 1
    A == 1
    GEN == 0
Output
    Filename Output.bdo
    Geo Detect
    Quantity Dose 
    Quantity Dose 
    Quantity AvgEnergy protons
